Privacy Policy for "DealerDroid - Texas Hold'em"

Last updated on September 12, 2023

1. Introduction

This privacy policy explains how "DealerDroid - Texas Hold'em" (hereinafter referred to as "the App") collects, uses, and protects personal data. The App collects and stores only very limited information to enhance user-friendliness and does not share any personal data with third parties.

2. Collected Data

The App collects and stores only the last entered player name locally on your device. This information is used exclusively to ensure that you do not have to re-enter your player name the next time you use the App.

3. Use of Collected Data

The collected data is used solely for the purpose mentioned above and is not shared with third parties. The data is used only to improve the user experience of the App.

4. Data Security

The security of your data is important to us. The collected data is stored on your device and is protected against unauthorized access. The App implements appropriate security measures to ensure the integrity and confidentiality of the data.

5. Changes to this Privacy Policy

This privacy policy may be updated from time to time to reflect changes in the App or privacy practices. Please check this privacy policy regularly for updates.

6. Contact

If you have any questions, comments, or concerns regarding this privacy policy or the privacy practices of the App, you can contact us at datenschutz(a)geesys.de.
